08:43.385 --> 08:46.781
eight pages of goat care instructions.

08:46.828 --> 08:48.511
"Drain glands at least three"...

08:48.536 --> 08:50.793
No. No, no, no.
I'm not draining any glands.

08:50.818 --> 08:52.667
No, Mike. We made this worse.

08:52.692 --> 08:54.589
Oh, hell yeah. Yeah,
it's much, much worse.

08:54.614 --> 08:55.897
We have to find that bunker.

08:56.819 --> 08:59.022
And it's good!

08:59.047 --> 09:00.478
- Hey.
- Hey. Can I um...

09:00.503 --> 09:02.509
clear some of this off,
whatever that is?

09:02.925 --> 09:04.274
Yeah. Whatever.

09:04.299 --> 09:05.439
Ow!

09:05.837 --> 09:07.275
Aah. I'm bleeding.

09:07.300 --> 09:10.282
Aah, I guess paper really
does beat... rock.

09:10.307 --> 09:12.743
Make sure you are banging
back some electrolytes, okay?

09:12.768 --> 09:14.209
- Yeah.
- You're doing a lot of flexing.

09:14.233 --> 09:15.443
Hey, hey, hey, hey.

09:15.468 --> 09:16.873
- Holy smokes.
- Whoa.

09:16.898 --> 09:18.013
Who's the lucky guy?

09:18.038 --> 09:20.763
Me? Is it me? No, I know.

09:20.788 --> 09:21.795
No, no. Okay.

09:21.820 --> 09:24.974
So, Sierra called me a "Buck-Snore"...

09:25.413 --> 09:26.943
